article_title: Insurers Still Bullish On Obamacare's Medicaid Expansion

article_metadata.description: The announcement by health insurer Centene that it would make a larger 2015 profit builds momentum for the Affordable Care Act’s Medicaid expansion even as some insurers struggle subsidizing uninsured Americans on public exchanges with commercial coverage. It’s also a good sign for industry consolidation because Centene said its 2016 guidance assumes [...]
